      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. the issue is that the losses are happening in areas of the warehouse that are relatively well-monitored, but we still can't find a clear pattern for where the items are going. it almost feels like they're just vanishing into thin air. what are some other ways to investigate these \"ghost\" discrepancies?",
